ed. Poetics meet Pharmaceutics.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aLiterary StudiesxLiterary Studies, general. 0aLiterature and medicine. 0aLiterature, ModernxHistory and criticism. 0aMass media and literature. 0aMedicine in literature. 0aPoisons in literature. 0aTherapeutics in literature. 4aAllgemeine Literaturwissenschaft. 4aDigitalisierung. 4aDroge. 4aGift. 4aHeilmittel. 4aLiteraturtheorie. 4aLiteraturwissenschaft. 4aMedien. 4aMedientheorie. 4aMedienwandel. 4aPharmaka. 4aPoetologie. 4aRezeption. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh  aDigitalization.  aDrug.  aGeneral Literature Studies.  aLiterary Studies.  aMedia Theory.  aMedia.  aMedication.  aPerception.  aPharmaceuticals.  aPoetology.  aPoison.  aTheory of Literature.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2015z9783110438673oZDB-23-DKU08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839428306zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839428306423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839428306/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DKUb2015  aZDB-23-TGPc2014d2016